import { Box, Container, TextField } from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";

function SchoolForm(props) {
  return (
    <>
      <Container maxWidth="sm">
        <Box mt={3}>
          <TextField
            id="outlined-basic"
            label="No. Of Students"
            variant="outlined"
            fullWidth
          />
        </Box>
        <Box mt={3}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            variant="outlined"
            placeholder="Total Classes"
            required
            size="medium"
          ></TextField>
        </Box>
        <Box mt={3}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            variant="outlined"
            placeholder="Expense "
            required
            size="medium"
          ></TextField>
        </Box>
        <Box mt={3}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            variant="outlined"
            placeholder="Revenue"
            required
            size="medium"
          ></TextField>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}

export default SchoolForm;
